Nollywood actress, Chinonso Arubayi, has informed intending suitors that she now accepts fuel instead of flowers and chocolates. Read what she wrote below, Chinonso Arubayi Shares Stunning Pictures Of Herself And Son “Nigeria which way forward? My fuel tank is now on E, and I am now outside. Dear intending suitors, this is an update that I no longer have coconut head,” she wrote. “I have started accepting fuel, please don’t send me flowers and chocolates. I now accept fuel and fuel money.”